16
00:01:05.815 --> 00:01:06.983 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Shinichi.</i>

17
00:01:07.817 --> 00:01:10.737 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Migi, you never change.</i>

18
00:01:10.820 --> 00:01:12.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>You're so blunt.</i>

19
00:01:14.908 --> 00:01:20.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>But I'm really glad you're alive, Migi.</i>

20
00:01:23.708 --> 00:01:26.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
