21
00:01:26.711 --> 00:01:28.171 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>You look like you.</i>

22
00:01:28.254 --> 00:01:31.508 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Before, you were totally different.</i>

23
00:01:31.591 --> 00:01:33.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I think it was like…</i>

24
00:01:33.343 --> 00:01:34.636 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Never mind.

25
00:01:34.719 --> 00:01:37.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
