26
00:01:37.764 --> 00:01:39.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>What do you mean?</i>

27
00:01:40.016 --> 00:01:41.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
