28
00:01:41.976 --> 00:01:43.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Sleep?</i>

29
00:01:43.853 --> 00:01:46.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
