30
00:01:46.356 --> 00:01:47.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It's a different kind of sleep.

31
00:01:48.024 --> 00:01:49.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>This time, it'll be for a while longer.</i>

32
00:01:50.068 --> 00:01:52.153 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>It may very well last until I die.</i>

33
00:01:52.237 --> 00:01:53.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>In other words,</i>

34
00:01:53.279 --> 00:01:56.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
