36
00:01:58.952 --> 00:02:00.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I don't get what you mean!</i>

37
00:02:00.286 --> 00:02:03.915 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
