has been altered yet again.

38
00:02:03.998 --> 00:02:09.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
In particular, my time spent in a lucid
dream of sorts within Gotou's body,

39
00:02:09.838 --> 00:02:15.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
where I felt alone yet not alone,
has been a major factor in that change.

40
00:02:15.301 --> 00:02:17.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>But Migi.</i>

41
00:02:17.720 --> 00:02:20.390 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Not only did I obtain a massive
amount of information at once

42
00:02:20.473 --> 00:02:23.977 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
but I also became capable of pursuing
many lines of thought in parallel.

43
00:02:24.060 --> 00:02:26.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I now want to shut out
all other information for a while

44
00:02:26.521 --> 00:02:28.064 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and see what I can accomplish
with the material

45
00:02:28.148 --> 00:02:29.774 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I currently have at my disposal.

46
00:02:29.858 --> 00:02:33.027 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So, I will stop all surface activity
for the time being.

47
00:02:33.111 --> 00:02:36.030 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>What? I can't believe I'm hearing this.</i>

48
00:02:36.114 --> 00:02:38.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>You were always so curious.</i>

49
00:02:38.241 --> 00:02:39.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>What's wrong?</i>

50
00:02:39.701 --> 00:02:42.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Aren't there still all kinds of things</i>
<i>you don't know?</i>

51
00:02:42.996 --> 00:02:44.247 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
