Well, I'll put it this way.

53
00:02:45.874 --> 00:02:48.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I'm going to try heading in
a different direction.

54
00:02:49.043 --> 00:02:52.714 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
A direction that's slightly different
from your world.

55
00:02:52.797 --> 00:02:55.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I don't understand.</i>

56
00:02:55.258 --> 00:03:00.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Shinichi, I want you to think of me
as a dream.

57
00:03:00.847 --> 00:03:04.309 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
That's why I'm saying
goodbye to you in one.

58
00:03:05.268 --> 00:03:06.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>What are you talking about?</i>

59
00:03:06.644 --> 00:03:09.522 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>All the days I spent with you,</i>
<i>all the times we helped each other,</i>

60
00:03:09.606 --> 00:03:11.107 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>they weren't a dream!</i>

61
00:03:11.190 --> 00:03:12.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You're right.

62
00:03:12.442 --> 00:03:14.903 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
The horrific events in your vicinity,

63
00:03:15.695 --> 00:03:18.197 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
the deaths of many people,
did happen in reality.

64
00:03:20.366 --> 00:03:21.451 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Mom!</i>

65
00:03:21.534 --> 00:03:22.785 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Mom!</i>

66
00:03:22.869 --> 00:03:24.913 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Why is Mom here?</i>

67
00:03:24.996 --> 00:03:28.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It's a mental projection you generated
upon hearing me talk about deaths.

68
00:03:29.417 --> 00:03:34.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Oh, so this is how your mother
appears to you in your mind.

69
00:03:34.881 --> 00:03:36.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>What?</i>

70
00:03:36.299 --> 00:03:37.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>What do you mean?</i>

71
00:03:41.012 --> 00:03:42.013 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>What's this?</i>

72
00:03:44.057 --> 00:03:47.644 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
They're all very different from how
I perceived them in my mind's eye.

73
00:03:48.770 --> 00:03:50.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Show how you see me.

74
00:03:53.233 --> 00:03:54.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

75
00:03:54.567 --> 00:03:56.569 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
