76
00:03:58.821 --> 00:04:00.990 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Well, so that's that.

77
00:04:01.658 --> 00:04:04.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
