of traffic accidents.

86
00:04:44.575 --> 00:04:46.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Wait!</i>

87
00:04:46.286 --> 00:04:48.871 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>So I can't ever talk to you again?</i>

88
00:04:48.955 --> 00:04:50.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Forever?</i>

89
00:04:50.873 --> 00:04:52.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Possibly.

90
00:04:52.250 --> 00:04:55.586 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
