92
00:05:02.552 --> 00:05:04.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>This is too much.</i>

93
00:05:04.637 --> 00:05:06.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>How can you spring this on me?</i>

94
00:05:07.223 --> 00:05:12.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
