about me along with this dream.

96
00:05:20.653 --> 00:05:23.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yes, I'm sure you can.

97
00:05:25.658 --> 00:05:28.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Listen, when you wake up in the morning,

98
00:05:28.786 --> 00:05:31.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
