100
00:05:34.375 --> 00:05:35.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Migi.</i>

101
00:05:37.045 --> 00:05:40.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Thank you for everything, Shinichi.</i>

102
00:06:12.371 --> 00:06:14.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
