103
00:06:14.207 --> 00:06:15.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Idiot!

104
00:06:19.587 --> 00:06:21.172 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You idiot.

105
00:06:32.350 --> 00:06:36.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
