112
00:06:52.286 --> 00:06:54.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Not that I really want to.

113
00:06:55.623 --> 00:06:58.751 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
