in your way, so we'll take off.

114
00:06:58.835 --> 00:07:01.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Later, guys!

115
00:07:02.088 --> 00:07:03.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
