118
00:07:14.308 --> 00:07:15.935 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hurry up and catch up, then.

119
00:07:16.018 --> 00:07:17.812 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
