120
00:07:22.900 --> 00:07:24.694 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Studying after failing</i>
<i>college entrance exams</i>

121
00:07:24.777 --> 00:07:28.281 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>is like taking a nap</i>
<i>in a park on a sunny day</i>

122
00:07:28.364 --> 00:07:30.700 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>compared to all the crazy stuff</i>
<i>that came before.</i>

123
00:07:31.325 --> 00:07:33.453 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Nothing's happened lately.</i>

124
00:07:34.162 --> 00:07:38.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I haven't come across a single sign</i>
<i>of the parasites around here.</i>

125
00:07:39.500 --> 00:07:41.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I talked about</i>
<i>what might've happened to them</i>

126
00:07:42.378 --> 00:07:45.506 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>with Uda-san in Izu over the phone, once,</i>

127
00:07:46.507 --> 00:07:49.719 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>but I didn't tell him about Migi.</i>

128
00:07:50.261 --> 00:07:54.056 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Migi's "disappearance" is unique,</i>
<i>even among his kind.</i>

129
00:07:56.559 --> 00:08:00.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Migi, in the end,</i>
<i>I never did understand you.</i>

130
00:08:01.522 --> 00:08:02.773 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>But that's okay.</i>

131
00:08:02.857 --> 00:08:05.985 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I'm sure you're walking</i>
<i>in places unknown to me.</i>

132
00:08:06.944 --> 00:08:09.906 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>The many battles we fought together,</i>

133
00:08:10.531 --> 00:08:13.576 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>they weren't for the sake of Earth</i>
<i>or anything.</i>

134
00:08:14.285 --> 00:08:16.287 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>It was for humanity.</i>

135
00:08:17.038 --> 00:08:19.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Or, really, more for me as an individual.</i>

136
00:08:21.751 --> 00:08:23.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>In the end,</i>

137
00:08:23.586 --> 00:08:27.048 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
