00:08:27.715 --> 00:08:29.050 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Of course not.</i>

139
00:08:29.133 --> 00:08:31.511 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>It wasn't possible from the beginning.</i>

140
