00:17:24.668 --> 00:17:28.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>You carried me and protected me</i>
<i>with everything you had.</i>

289
00:17:28.547 --> 00:17:31.508 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Sure, you might not be "normal",</i>

290
00:17:31.592 --> 00:17:32.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>but you're human!</i>

291
00:17:33.510 --> 00:17:36.597 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Humans think all life is precious!

292
00:17:36.680 --> 00:17:38.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You're the monster, jerk!

293
00:17:38.515 --> 00:17:40.100 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That's enough, Satomi.

294
00:17:40.184 --> 00:17:43.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Izumi-kun, just go!

295
00:17:44.730 --> 00:17:46.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sure, fine.

296
00:17:46.440 --> 00:17:48.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Go call the cops, kid.

297
00:17:49.068 --> 00:17:51.820 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I think this girl's going to be more fun.

298
00:17:51.904 --> 00:17:56.325 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I'll have fun taking this toy apart
while I wait.

299
00:17:56.408 --> 00:17:59.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
This will probably be
the last fun I ever have.

300
00:17:59.703 --> 00:18:03.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It's always more fun
taking apart the spunky ones.

301
00:18:04.875 --> 00:18:06.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Shinichi-kun!

302
00:18:08.003 --> 00:18:09.546 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I…

303
00:18:09.630 --> 00:18:12.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I was always trying to catch up with you.

304
00:18:12.716 --> 00:18:15.761 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But you're so fast,

305
00:18:15.844 --> 00:18:18.097 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
you kept walking off into worlds
I didn't understand.

306
00:18:19.723 --> 00:18:22.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I was the one left behind.

307
00:18:23.477 --> 00:18:26.438 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
But now that I've finally caught up
with you,

308
00:18:27.439 --> 00:18:31.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
it looks like I might've
actually gone too far ahead.

309
00:18:32.236 --> 00:18:34.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Stop!

310
00:18:34.404 --> 00:18:36.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I'll save her! I'll get to her in time!</i>

311
00:18:36.740 --> 00:18:39.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>That's right, I'm fast!</i>

312
00:18:39.493 --> 00:18:41.036 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I'm not a normal human being!</i>

313
00:18:41.829 --> 00:18:43.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>To me, he looks like he's frozen in time!</i>

314
00:18:44.832 --> 00:18:46.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>With my left, strike his knife hand up</i>

315
00:18:47.376 --> 00:18:49.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>and slam his jaw!</i>

316
00:18:50.838 --> 00:18:53.715 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Then, with my right…</i>

317
00:18:54.341 --> 00:18:58.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Toys are so easily broken.</i>

318
00:19:06.854 --> 00:19:10.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No. It can't be.

319
00:19:10.691 --> 00:19:12.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
This is too much.

320
00:19:13.277 --> 00:19:17.197 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Why does it always end like this?

321
00:19:20.450 --> 00:19:23.453 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>An organism I met in passing</i>
<i>and got to know</i>

322
00:19:23.537 --> 00:19:25.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>was suddenly dead.</i>

323
00:19:27.541 --> 00:19:31.336 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Why do I get sad when that happens?</i>

324
00:19:32.004 --> 00:19:35.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Well, that's because humans
have so much time on their hands.

325
00:19:35.924 --> 00:19:40.888 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But that's their greatest merit.

326
00:19:40.971 --> 00:19:43.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
An organism with time
to spare in their hearts,

327
00:19:43.974 --> 00:19:45.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
how wonderful is that?

328
00:19:45.934 --> 00:19:49.938 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
So, quit whining already.

329
00:19:50.564 --> 00:19:52.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I'm getting tired,
so you can do the holding.

330
00:19:56.612 --> 00:19:57.988 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Satomi!</i>

331
00:20:00.657 --> 00:20:02.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I got to her in time?</i>

332
00:20:02.409 --> 00:20:04.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Migi!</i>

333
00:20:14.254 --> 00:20:15.214 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You okay?

334
00:20:18.175 --> 00:20:20.594 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Thanks, Migi.</i>

335
00:20:20.677 --> 00:20:22.346 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>You're still alive!</i>

336
00:20:24.014 --> 00:20:26.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Did Satomi see Migi?</i>

337
00:20:27.476 --> 00:20:28.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Oh, well.</i>

338
00:20:29.019 --> 00:20:31.605 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I don't mind if she saw him.</i>

339
00:20:33.941 --> 00:20:35.567 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What a beautiful sky.

340
00:20:37.027 --> 00:20:40.489 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Do you remember the puppy that died?

341
00:20:41.240 --> 00:20:43.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'd thrown him away in a trash can.

342
00:20:43.951 --> 00:20:45.869 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I forgot to tell you before,

343
00:20:46.745 --> 00:20:48.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
but after I thought about it for a while,

344
00:20:49.373 --> 00:20:51.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I moved him and buried him under a tree.

345
00:20:52.209 --> 00:20:53.460 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I know.

346
00:20:55.003 --> 00:20:57.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You did that because you're…

347
00:20:59.883 --> 00:21:02.427 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You're Shinichi-kun.

348
00:21:08.308 --> 00:21:10.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
There are three people
on the ground there, too!

349
00:21:10.936 --> 00:21:12.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Three, he says.

350
00:21:12.729 --> 00:21:14.690 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeah, they think we're dead.

351
00:21:19.736 --> 00:21:23.031 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>We were all born here on Earth.</i>

352
00:21:24.408 --> 00:21:28.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>We try to keep understanding</i>
<i>each other along these tiny points</i>

353
00:21:28.287 --> 00:21:30.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>until they accumulate.</i>

354
00:21:31.957 --> 00:21:35.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>We try to get closer to someone else</i>

355
00:21:36.586 --> 00:21:38.755 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>until our lives someday end.</i>

